title: CJEUs
extract: The Court of Justice of the European Union (CJEU) (French: Cour de justice de l'Union européenne) is the institution of the European Union (EU) that encompasses the whole judiciary. ... It has a sui generis court system, meaning "of its own kind", and is a supranational institution.
